videos.description: Marine Johannes fires and sinks the early three ball for the Liberty.
videos.headline: Johannes splashes the trey

videos.description: Sun's Courtney Williams crashes the board for an offensive rebound, then makes a beautiful dish to Alyssa Thomas for the strong and-1 bucket.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Williams grabs offensive rebound, dishes to Thomas for strong and-1) 2022/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams grabs offensive rebound, dishes to Thomas for strong and-1

videos.description: Marine Johannes goes off one leg and knocks down a massive triple to contribute to Liberty's 10-0 run.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Johannes sinks the massive triple off of one leg) 2022/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Johannes sinks the massive buzzer-beating triple off of one leg

videos.description: DiJonai Carrington hooks a sweet pass to Jonquel Jones who lays in the bucket and extends the Sun's run to 11-0.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Carrington hooks a sweet pass to Jones for the bucket) 2022/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carrington hooks a sweet pass to Jones for the bucket

videos.description: Natasha Howard remains strong down low and floats in the and-1 bucket for Liberty.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Howard puts the moves on her defender and sinks the and-1) 2022/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Howard puts the moves on her defender and sinks the and-1

videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu gets past the defender and nails the 3-pointer for Liberty.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Ionescu sets up for the 3 and nails it) 2022/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ionescu sets up for the 3 and nails it

videos.description: Natisha Hiedeman drives the ball to the hoop for the bucket and the foul.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Hiedeman drives strong to the hoop for and-1 opportunity) 2022/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hiedeman drives strong to the hoop for and-1 opportunity

videos.description: Sami Whitcomb fakes out the defender and pulls up for her fourth 3-pointer of the night for the Liberty.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Whitcomb sinks her 4th triple of the night) 2022/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Whitcomb sinks her 4th triple of the night
